        {
            "title": "安克創新暗盤中段較招股價低逾6%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">安克創新(00668)將於本周四掛牌，成為2026年下半年首隻登場新股。該股暗盤中段暫時表現則未能沖高，暫較招股價低逾6%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">根據輝立交易平台資料，截至下午約5時26分，安克創新暗盤報92.9元，較招股價低6.46%；富途交易平台顯示的暗盤暫報92.65元，也較招股價低6.72%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/16271249-%e5%ae%89%e5%85%8b%e5%89%b5%e6%96%b0%e6%9a%97%e7%9b%a4%e4%b8%ad%e6%ae%b5%e8%bc%83%e6%8b%9b%e8%82%a1%e5%83%b9%e4%bd%8e%e9%80%be6",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/06/00668.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-06-30 17:30:56",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "華潤飲料擬斥不逾5.3億元回購",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">華潤飲料(02460)公布，董事會決定行使回購授權，動用不超過5.3億元在公開市場回購。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：華潤飲料官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20240423_FI_02460_source-web_fb.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：華潤飲料官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20240423_FI_02460_source-web_fb.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：華潤飲料官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">董事會明表，相信公司目前的財務資源足以支持實施上述回購計劃，同時保持穩健的財務狀況，以支持本集團的業務增長。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">董事會亦認為，股份的當前成交價格並未反映內在價值及實際業務前景，有關情況是公司購回股份的良機。回購計劃亦反映了董事會對公司前景的信心，以及對提升股東回報的重視。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/16271131-%e8%8f%af%e6%bd%a4%e9%a3%b2%e6%96%99%e6%93%ac%e6%96%a5%e4%b8%8d%e9%80%be5-3%e5%84%84%e5%85%83%e5%9b%9e%e8%b3%bc",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250728_FI_source-web_02460-2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-06-30 17:11:55",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "嘉里\"緹外\"成功標售3伙  成交額6.6億元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=16263384&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 150px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">嘉里(00683)發展的九龍半山豪宅緹外，成功標售3伙，總成交金額達6.6億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">第一個單位第1座2樓B室連裝修分層大宅，實用面積4432方呎，連兩個住宅車位，以2.15億元售出，實用呎價約48511元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">第二個單位為第6座地下A室連裝修花園大宅，實用面積3466方呎，連一個住宅車位，以2億元售出，實用呎價約57703元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">第三個單位為第6座5樓B室分層大宅，實用面積4262方呎，連一個住宅車位，以2.45億元售出，實用呎價約57485元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">項目至今累售52伙，總成交金額衝破154億元，平均成交實用呎價約5.8萬元。項目尚餘10個分層大宅及2個頂層連天台特色大宅待售。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/16263384-%e5%98%89%e9%87%8c%e7%b7%b9%e5%a4%96%e6%88%90%e5%8a%9f%e6%a8%99%e5%94%ae3%e4%bc%99-%e6%88%90%e4%ba%a4%e9%a1%8d6-6%e5%84%84%e5%85%83",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/pp_new-flat-transaction_fb.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-06-30 17:06:41",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
